        probability - The probability that any pair of nodes is connected.

      • readFile

        public static Graph readFile(java.lang.String name)
        Reads in a file specifying the graph. This file must be formatted as follows: each line specifies an edge by the name of the nodes it connects. Each line must contain two node names, separated by a tab. The method fails if any line contains less than two parts separated by a tab, parts beyond the first two in a line are ignored.
        Parameters:
        name - The filename of the graph file.
        Returns:
        The graph constructed from the file.
